  "title": "Allow to control autoHideContainer behavior",
  "body": "The default behavior of autoHideContainer is widget based.\n\nGiven the widget, we will apply some rules that ultimately will decide if we want to show or hide the widget.\n\nSome of those rules, may or may not make sense given the user use case. See #986.\n\nI believe we should allow the user to override that default behavior.\n",
